{
  "stem": "20142.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Very devoted to, to the classes, and they did enjoy when they getting a response from the class of absorbing the material that they were delivering.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that you switch, but if you wanted to continue, either you could go after public school to a vocational school and learn a trade, or you wanted to continue in studies, they you continued through gymnasium, and lyceum and then to university.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The gymnasium had four years of classes, including Latin, and Hebrew, and [NON-ENGLISH] and Jewish history.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Latin was needed because it was compulsory curriculum of the Polish government.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after the four years, you received the small matriculation papers, and you could continue to lyceum, the final two years for preparation for the colleges or universities.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with good grades, you did not have to go through examination to enter any of the universities.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You were automatically accepted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even in some of the universities outside of the Poland, there were accepting people from our schools in good-- with good grades.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the public?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or, it's a quite great amount of learning, and we did not have the possibility of learning of algebra, geometry, trigonometry, history, geography.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These things were lumped together with-- history and geography were combined into one unit that you learned about the part of the world and there was history involved.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was arranged in such a way that you could absorb this material, providing that you wanted to learn.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the public school, there was a certain amount of pressure, but not with the same amount as you experience in probably in the gymnasium, in the high school.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our high school were rigorous.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
